Mark D. Okerstrom 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President of Operations and Chief Financial Officer at EXPEDIA INC, Mark D. Okerstrom  made $18,186,390 in total compensation.  Of this total $750,000 was received as a salary, $750,000 was received as a bonus, $16,632,057 was received in stock options, $0 was awarded as stock and $54,333 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


