Insider Activity


Individual




Mark D. Okerstrom



Mr. Mark D. Okerstrom is Chief Financial Officer & Executive VP-Operations at Expedia, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at HomeAway, Inc.
Mr. Okerstrom was previously employed as Attorney-Mergers & Acquisitions by Freshfields Bruckhaus Deringer LLP, a Principal by UBS Ltd., and Strategy Consultant by Bain & Co., Inc.
He received his graduate degree from the University of British Columbia and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



